column2: SELECT   s.z as s_z,    gi.z as gi_z, gi.z_err as gi_zerr, gi.z_warning as gi_zwarning, gi.specObjID, gi.ra as gi_ra, gi.dec as gi_dec, gi.spectrotype, gi.subclass, gi.reliable as gi_reliable,   ge.bptclass into mydb.MyTable from galSpecInfo AS gi     LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON gi.specObjID = ge.specObjID     LEFT JOIN specObj as s ON gi.specObjID = s.specObjID
